The  ENTRAÑA SKIRT STEAK TACOS from @panca_restaurant! 🌮🤤🥩
🔥 House Tortillas w/ Skirt Steak, Pico de Gallo, and Avocado.
Happy #TacoTuesday! 🙏
📍: @panca_restaurant
🌆: West Village, NYC
📱: Follow 5boroughfoodie on TikTok!

The delicious VODKA-RONI PIZZA PIE from Bellucci Pizza! 🍕🤤🍕
🔥 Fresh Mozzarella, and-cut Pepperoni, topped w/ their famous Vodka Sauce, fresh ground black pepper & grated 18-month aged Parmigiano Reggiano.
📍: Bellucci Pizza
🌇: Queens, NYC 📱: Follow 5boroughfoodie on TikTok!
